-------XGenAnalytics Sentiment Analysis-------

Sentiment Analysis of Unstructured Text using Naive Bayes Classifier. 
Lexicon Dictionary provided here is just a sample. Please add your own dictionary and scores in the file data/lex_dict.csv before running the function.

##"Use code with caution - No Warranty or Guarantee is provided as mentioned in the License"##

Dependencies:
R>2
libraries: tm, plyr, Rstem

Usage:
xga_sentiment(unstructured_text)

Eg: xga_sentiment("destiny devotee !")
